text = "NOTES:

elitrics, have spies - mentioned once in Gus book
Utorios, nonexistent nation of hunter-gatherers

Bauland: Fish, Big Insects (area where big animals developed)
Lanti Archipelago: Indingenous people
Ruu Bo: Half hot, Half cold todoroki ass (home to angel/devils could be two kingdoms or one, could be racism or no)
Terranica: Bouldaaks (nation of weird biomes)

Pustan: Cowboys, Palms, Utorios (dead), Elitrics, Salzabar (arabs), has the River of Life, group of nolaka that are nomads? like life magicians that settled down"
